sentences: He was the director of the Wrocław Philharmonic from 1965 to 1968 and founded the Wratislavia Cantans festival.
He was awarded the Minister of Culture and Art Award, 2nd class in 1965.
He received the "Orpheus" critics' award in 1968 and 1971.
In 1969 he was awarded the annual Polish Composers' Union prize and in 1974 he received the State Award, 1st class.
